{"tid":1607571,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果個49歲廢中當年無做警察，今日就唔洗死！","createTime":"2019-10-01T01:41:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T03:06:15.000Z","uid":42188,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"6cd05fe1577300105474ca257b0b90799acd56e2","tid":1607571,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T01:41:21.000Z","msg":"香港文匯報訊（記者 蕭景源）暴徒亂港近4個月，警隊3萬警員連續奮戰止暴，身心俱疲未言退。一名駐守特遣隊的老差骨，在過去3個月，因同袍抽調參加平暴，和其他留守警署負責平日滅罪任務的同袍一樣，一人身兼幾個人的工作，近月常加班和捱夜，其間更短時間替更作防暴警衝在第一線。他近日患感冒仍堅持上班，懷疑疲勞過度觸發隱疾，昨日被發現在家中離世，成為暴徒作孽的犧牲者。"},{"pid":"c2743a96ff607a8fb297e4a49ac05852acbfe07e","tid":1607571,"uid":245101,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T01:47:56.000Z","msg":"暴徒作孽咪就係班警察囉"},{"pid":"d63f185e7c5571c2d571a47f88f61e6f6594049e","tid":1607571,"uid":50744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:06:15.000Z","msg":"個別事件"},{"pid":"e706ffd05048cec600b583f05c0f1fc0add74cbc","tid":1607571,"uid":283792,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:08:10.000Z","msg":"自作孽不可活"},{"pid":"d18080654f2eea73295a028f16d70e0d9a918a6b","tid":1607571,"uid":7322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:08:53.000Z","msg":"祝香港警察日日有今日  之後無聽朝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d63c4dbe1fdc19d6faa11860e6f590488388cbe1","tid":1607571,"uid":92299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:09:35.000Z","msg":"聽日一戰，睇到呢個手勢就向前衝 打返轉頭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1607145\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1607145</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"873c0470b2dd9670e4e92d89ecb38d087f062c97","tid":1607571,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:10:06.000Z","msg":"你行得正企得正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"